Package: screenwerk
Type: Package
Title: A modular library with a set of tools for the design and analysis of 
    drug combination screens
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2022-11-03
Authors@R: person("Robert", "Hanes", ,"robert.hanes@medisin.uio.no",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6544-2182"))
Description: screenwerk is an R package that consists of multiple functions 
    that can be used to (a) set up a drug screen and generate a dispensing 
    file, (b) read raw measurements and consolidate different data sets, 
    (c) perform quality control, (d) analyze, and (e) report and visualize the 
    results. 
